metadata.name: The Road to the Clouds
metadata.description:
This work illustrates our lives. Each of us has to travel a different path before we can reach our goal. 
Each peak in the painting symbolizes a person's journey. From the smallest, to the biggest goals in life. 
And it's up to you to decide how close you get to your goal...

This is the 1st NFT in a collection of 6 that have been produced in a single unique print run.

image size: 6000 x 9600px
